<plot>This thriller is about a vacation cruise in the Gulf of Mexico, during which some of the passengers find an ancient Egyptian sarcophagus in an underwater cavern. Instead of wasting time explaining what Egyptian ruins are doing so far from Northern Africa, the writers decide to make things easy by making the coffin's occupant none other than the Devil himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?119765</url></doc>
